name: Jennifer Aniston
description:
Model of Jennifer Aniston. Took a while to figure out the best way to prepare and train but I think I figured it out. Hope you like it. It should be accurate to the yonfer Jennifer yet flexible for styling.

For even better results you can combine this LoRA with the corresponding TI by mixing at 50/50: Jennifer Anniston | Stable Diffusion TextualInversion | Civitai

Or this other TI: 90s Jennifer Aniston | Stable Diffusion TextualInversion | Civitai

Utilise the kohya-ss/sd-webui-additional-networks (github.com) in auto1111 to load the LoRA model. You can also blend it with other LoRA models for a diverse range of poses.
This model can be combined to the TI embedding I will attach with the model.

Use DPM++ SDE Karras sampling
